title: A$AP Mobb and Donell Rawlings Interview
itunes:title: A$AP Mobb and Donell Rawlings Interview
description:
Today on the show we had the hilarious Donell Rawlings where he might've gotten a little bothered by Charlamagne's butt mold... The entire A$AP Mob also stopped by and spoke about Rocky's arrest in Sweeden and the legacy Yam's left on the group. Donkey of the day went to none other! Than ooooleeeeeeeeeeee BJ, Mister Odell Beckham Jr.
